how important the big gesture is.

09:30.990 --> 09:33.079
I get romance. I just don't think

09:33.080 --> 09:34.912
you need shock and
awe to prove it.

09:34.913 --> 09:36.053
All... What do you think, Scotty?

09:36.054 --> 09:37.023
Me? Mm-hmm.

09:37.024 --> 09:38.323
I'd take anything at this point.

09:38.324 --> 09:39.383
Kevin chose this week to

09:39.384 --> 09:42.912
attend a legal convention.
I'm sorry, man.

09:43.009 --> 09:44.828
Yeah. He didn't even send flowers.

09:45.022 --> 09:46.390
Hell, even Olivia sent a card,

09:46.391 --> 09:48.051
and we haven't even
adopted her yet.

09:48.101 --> 09:51.784
Kevin loves you.
I promise. Thank you.

09:52.311 --> 09:54.929
Oh, my G... I feel like
I'm in a women's bathroom.

09:55.045 --> 09:57.670
What is it about this holiday
that just drags estrogen

09:57.671 --> 09:58.532
out of dudes?

09:58.533 --> 10:01.862
Oh, that is so sexist. Love
