10:17.253 --> 10:19.060
I can't help you. Okay.

10:22.894 --> 10:26.142
If you're willing to forget
the big grand gesture...

10:27.990 --> 10:29.220
Okay, what do I do?

10:29.221 --> 10:31.135
I have a suggestion,
and Sarah's gonna love it.

10:31.136 --> 10:32.000
Trust me.

10:33.210 --> 10:35.007
Nora, what are you doing here?

