in old age. That's all.

11:09.728 --> 11:10.544
Found 'em.

11:11.170 --> 11:14.069
Saul, why don't you
live in the moment

11:14.070 --> 11:16.760
instead of constantly
focusing on the past?

11:16.761 --> 11:18.731
Oh, really? Look who's talking.

11:19.152 --> 11:22.468
Why don't you put away
your high school yearbook?

