12:22.361 --> 12:23.496
Were you in love with him?

12:27.828 --> 12:30.960
Well, you tell me.
Are you in love with Jonathan?

12:30.961 --> 12:32.809
Jonathan? What, are you crazy?

12:32.810 --> 12:34.051
What do you mean?
Where are you going?

12:34.052 --> 12:35.858
I have to get back to the studio.

12:36.000 --> 12:37.419
Be sure and lock
up when you leave.

12:37.420 --> 12:39.128
Well, hang on.
I'm gonna go with you.

12:39.129 --> 12:41.288
Come on. My car is blocking
